tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE TrainingData (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    state TEXT,
    action TEXT,
    reward FLOAT,
    next_state TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE training_data (
  data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  state_vector TEXT,
  action_vector TEXT,
  reward FLOAT,
  next_state_vector TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE training_history (
    training_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    training_time TIMESTAMP,
    loss FLOAT,
    accuracy FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE PreprocessedDataForRLModels (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  data_column1 TEXT,
  data_column2 TEXT,
  data_column3 DECIMAL,
  data_column4 DATE
)

CREATE TABLE PreprocessedDataForActions (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  action_column1 TEXT,
  action_column2 TEXT,
  action_column3 DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE Rewards (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  reward_value DECIMAL,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE ModelParameters (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  parameter_name TEXT,
  parameter_value TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE ModelHistory (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model_id INT,
  history_data JSON
)
